  "instructions": [
    "Press tofu to remove excess moisture, then cube it.",
    "In a bowl mix miso paste, soy sauce, sesame oil, mustard powder, red chilli powder, lime juice, and coconut milk into a smooth sauce.",
    "Toss tofu cubes in the sauce, cover, and marinate for 10 minutes.",
    "Cook rice noodles according to package directions, then drain and set aside.",
    "Heat a nonstick pan over medium heat, add a splash of water, and stir-fry marinated tofu for 5 minutes until lightly browned.",
